-- China to Delay `Mini-QFII' Rules to Curb Bubble, Oriental Daily Reports
-- B y   K e l v i n   W o n g
-- 2010-10-24T22:45:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-24/china-to-delay-mini-qfii-rules-to-curb-bubble-oriental-daily-reports.html
China may delay the implementation
of rules for its “mini-QFII” pilot project until the end of
the year to prevent its stock market from overheating, the
Oriental Daily reported, citing unidentified people close to
regulators.  To contact the reporter on this story:
